  "prompt": "What position/job title in companies is comparable to the \"launcher\" Uber uses to launch in other cities?",
  "response": "The position or job title comparable to \"launcher\" at Uber, which focuses on launching operations in new markets or cities, is often referred to as a **\"Market Launch Manager,\" \"City Launch Lead,\" or \"Market Expansion Manager.\"** These roles typically involve overseeing the strategy and execution of launching services in new areas, including market research, regulatory compliance, local partnerships, and team building. \n\nIn some companies, you might also see titles such as **\"Business Development Manager,\" \"Regional Operations Manager,\" or \"Growth Manager,\"** as they often encompass similar responsibilities related to market entry and expansion.",
